  "monster": {
    "title": "Faneots.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Faneots has an armoured brown body with sparrow-like wings and a face from nightmares.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 174     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: +++      </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ +    </lightgrey>                \n<darkgrey>    rF: ...     </darkgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ∞        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><darkgrey>rElec: .        </darkgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 160% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 69% to hit with your hands and 56% to hit with your bite, slice, and slice.\nIt has about 48% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     36          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeted by:\n  your orb of fire\n  your dread lich\n  your green draconian monk\n  your dread lich\n  your orb of fire\n  your Killer Klown\n  your Orb Guardian\n  your Killer Klown\n  your purple draconian shifter\n  your black draconian\n  your Orb Guardian\n  your yellow draconian annihilator\n  your Orb Guardian\n  your Brimstone Fiend\n  your Tzitzimitl",
    "quote": "",
